                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000003bdf80c9-44d4-428c-8ebe-98c69e4ae4dc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({\underset{S}{M{\left(OH\right)}_{2}}}\rightarrow {\underset{S\ \ \ \ }{{M}^{2+}}}\ +{\underset{2S}{2O{H}^{-}}};\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003bdf80c9-44d4-428c-8ebe-98c69e4ae4dc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000015cb2dca-7bf6-4f66-bb33-46e55ace9aae" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\({K}_{sp}=\left[ {M}^{2+}\right] \left[ O{H}^{-}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000115cb2dca-7bf6-4f66-bb33-46e55ace9aae"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=S\times {\left(2S\right)}^{2}⇒4{S}^{3}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000015cb2dca-7bf6-4f66-bb33-46e55ace9aae {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000115cb2dca-7bf6-4f66-bb33-46e55ace9aae {font-family: SolaimanLipi;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ae3c7a78-28e3-45e4-bbdd-7d657c9f73c8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ae3c7a78-28e3-45e4-bbdd-7d657c9f73c8">GLv‡b</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ae3c7a78-28e3-45e4-bbdd-7d657c9f73c8">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(5\times {10}^{-16}=4{S}^{3}⇒S=5\times {10}^{-6}M;\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ae3c7a78-28e3-45e4-bbdd-7d657c9f73c8 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ae3c7a78-28e3-45e4-bbdd-7d657c9f73c8 {font-family: SutonnyMJ;font-style: normal;font-weight: