                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-00000088f893cf-7a45-4176-b270-7ca9bedc64af" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000188f893cf-7a45-4176-b270-7ca9bedc64af">AmxgZU&#216;q</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000188f893cf-7a45-4176-b270-7ca9bedc64af">, </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{{\left(x-1\right)}^{2}}{4}-\frac{{\left(y+3\right)}^{2}}{9}=0\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000188f893cf-7a45-4176-b270-7ca9bedc64af"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000088f893cf-7a45-4176-b270-7ca9bedc64af {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000188f893cf-7a45-4176-b270-7ca9bedc64af {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000cfdc9bfb-d377-44b9-b765-9d8d143ee33c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒\frac{x-1}{2}=±\frac{y+3}{3}⇒3x-3=±\left(2y+6\right)\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001cfdc9bfb-d377-44b9-b765-9d8d143ee33c"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000cfdc9bfb-d377-44b9-b765-9d8d143ee33c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001cfdc9bfb-d377-44b9-b765-9d8d143ee33c {font-family: SutonnyMJ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000091be7c13-c1ff-41b3-8e74-7ce6f8efb1fc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000191be7c13-c1ff-41b3-8e74-7ce6f8efb1fc">AmxgZU&#216;‡qi</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000191be7c13-c1ff-41b3-8e74-7ce6f8efb1fc"> </span><span class="pt-00000191be7c13-c1ff-41b3-8e74-7ce6f8efb1fc">mgxKiY</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000191be7c13-c1ff-41b3-8e74-7ce6f8efb1fc">, </span