                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000e1ec5bc1-a862-4c90-b521-e3c1a0c07bc7" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\frac{{x}^{2}}{16}-\frac{{y}^{2}}{9}=1\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e1ec5bc1-a862-4c90-b521-e3c1a0c07bc7"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000e1ec5bc1-a862-4c90-b521-e3c1a0c07bc7 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001e1ec5bc1-a862-4c90-b521-e3c1a0c07bc7 {font-family: ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008bc70bb3-7def-4188-a63e-6c00223b9844" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018bc70bb3-7def-4188-a63e-6c00223b9844"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(x=±\frac{a}{e}=±\frac{4}{\sqrt{\frac{16+9}{16}}}=±4\times \frac{4}{5}=±\frac{16}{5}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008bc70bb3-7def-4188-a63e-6c00223b9844 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018bc70bb3-7def-4188-a63e-6c00223b9844 {font-family: ;color: black;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000b7f23570-b467-4c80-8544-1e252b0171cc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(∴5x=±16\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b7f23570-b467-4c80-8544-1e252b0171cc"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(\left[ {a}^{2}=16,\ {b}^{2}=9,\ c=\sqrt{1+\frac{9}{16}}=\frac{5}{4}\right] \) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001b7f23570-b467-4c80-8544-1e252b0171c