                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 85 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-0000001fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260">He got into the </span><span class="pt-0000021fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260">running</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000011fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260"> train. Here the word ‘running’ is a/an-</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260 {margin-bottom: 0;line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;}span.pt-0000011fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000021fccd5e8-4690-4515-9f75-c680af45d260 {font-family: Times New Roman;text-decoration: underline;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
